According to experts , <COREF ID="2" TYPE="IDENT">Jupiter , which orbits the Sun like <COREF ID="8" TYPE="IDENT">the Earth</COREF></COREF> , is the largest planet in <COREF ID="10" TYPE="IDENT">the solar system</COREF> .
