The Chinese astronomy arena also places great importance on <COREF ID="9" TYPE="IDENT">this phenomenon of <COREF ID="1" TYPE="IDENT">the comet</COREF> colliding with <COREF ID="2" TYPE="IDENT">Jupiter</COREF></COREF> and will closely focus attention on <COREF ID="9" TYPE="IDENT">its</COREF> development and changes .
